    "description": "<strong>IONIA™</strong> 是一款单人动作冒险解谜 VR 游戏，旨在突破 PC VR 的极限。与受音乐启发的生物近距离接触，在探索古代遗迹时解开谜题，并使用基于音乐的魔法来拯救 Harpa，这是一种栖息地处于毁灭边缘的神话生物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1121140/extras/dede1c5feaee99b9bdda4e8f17eccd14.poster.avif?t=1674247954\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1121140/extras/dede1c5feaee99b9bdda4e8f17eccd14.webm?t=1674247954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1121140/extras/dede1c5feaee99b9bdda4e8f17eccd14.mp4?t=1674247954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Harpa 是爱奥尼亚森林的心脏和灵魂。每一棵树都被接近的 Tritone 军队砍伐和烧毁，她的精神变得虚弱。你和你的妹妹 Allegra 是 Ionia 勇敢的新英雄，开始寻求用音乐的力量治愈这个神话生物，以免为时已晚。当您跟随 Allegra 踏上拯救 Harpa 的旅程时，您很快就会发现您的一举一动都会对您周围的世界产生影响。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1121140/extras/d8315d45dfb166aeee9d3151f2579d8b.avif?t=1674247954\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br>ROTU Entertainment 很荣幸能够支持 Wildlife Warriors USA Inc。对于在 Steam 美国“应用程序”商店购买《宇宙的节奏：爱奥尼亚》，ROTU Entertainment 将把其总收益的 5% 捐赠给 Wildlife Warriors USA Inc。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1121140/extras/62ba5aa71fb3a4911dd9550659e36ef4.poster.avif?t=1674247954\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1121140/extras/62ba5aa71fb3a4911dd9550659e36ef4.webm?t=1674247954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1121140/extras/62ba5aa71fb3a4911dd9550659e36ef4.mp4?t=1674247954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>这款故事生动的 VR 游戏是令人惊叹的视觉和听觉逃脱，让您可以与独特的生物、角色和植物进行互动。聆听强大的 Brassaurus 的召唤，沿着地下河骑在巨龟的背上，解决音乐谜题，解锁更多等你探索。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1121140/extras/79eb479c9b0d9b58faa1e1576d2ceefc.poster.avif?t=1674247954\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1121140/extras/79eb479c9b0d9b58faa1e1576d2ceefc.webm?t=1674247954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1121140/extras/79eb479c9b0d9b58faa1e1576d2ceefc.mp4?t=1674247954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>一个充满互动植物和动物生命的奇幻世界等待探索。为发光的陶笛寻找和觅食食物。当您滑索穿过峡谷时，欣赏令人叹为观止的远景。在古树的树冠上攀爬蜿蜒的藤蔓。沐浴在水洞深处发出的生物荧光中。艾欧尼亚的世界将围绕着你。",
